<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 14 Jan 2024 09:10:43 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>台湾大选让世界市场松了一口气，但令当地投资者担忧</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/taiwan-election-relief-world-markets-concern-local-investors-2024-01-14/</link><description>台湾大选可能会缓解全球对台湾与中国关系的担忧，同时引发周一国内股市小幅抛售，因为投资者担心选举结果可能会阻碍经济政策。</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Jan 2024 08:26:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/taiwan-election-relief-world-markets-concern-local-investors-2024-01-14/</guid></item><item><title>中国外交官谴责外国政府就台湾大选后发表的言论</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinese-embassies-condemn-foreign-officials-over-taiwan-post-election-remarks-2024-01-14/</link><description>中国外交部和世界各地的大使馆本周末警告各国不要支持台湾民进党（DPP），并谴责祝贺台湾当选总统赖清德的外国政府。</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Jan 2024 07:56:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinese-embassies-condemn-foreign-officials-over-taiwan-post-election-remarks-2024-01-14/</guid></item><item><title>美国前官员将访问台湾进行大选后会谈</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/former-us-officials-visit-taiwan-post-election-talks-2024-01-14/</link><description>美国驻台北事实上的大使馆表示，两名前美国高级官员将于周日抵达台湾进行选举后会谈，并强调美国政府对台海和平的“长期利益”。</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Jan 2024 07:17:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/former-us-officials-visit-taiwan-post-election-talks-2024-01-14/</guid></item><item><title>朝鲜外相将访问俄罗斯 - 朝中社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/north-koreas-foreign-minister-visit-russia-kcna-2024-01-14/</link><description>朝鲜官方通讯社朝中社周日称，朝鲜外交部长崔善姬将于 1 月 15 日至 17 日访问俄罗斯。</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Jan 2024 07:16:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/north-koreas-foreign-minister-visit-russia-kcna-2024-01-14/</guid></item><item><title>中国比亚迪与巴西Sigma Lithium就供应协议进行谈判 - FT</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-byd-talks-with-brazils-sigma-lithium-supply-deal-ft-2024-01-14/</link><description>据英国《金融时报》周日报道，中国电动汽车制造商比亚迪已与巴西西格玛锂业就可能的供应协议、合资或收购进行了谈判。</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Jan 2024 06:56:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-byd-talks-with-brazils-sigma-lithium-supply-deal-ft-2024-01-14/</guid></item><item><title>台湾新总统面临中国压力、议会不占多数的“艰难”时期</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwans-new-president-faces-tough-time-with-china-pressure-no-parliament-2024-01-14/</link><description>台湾当选总统赖清德可能会面临艰难的四年任期，因为他没有获得议会多数席位，反对派希望重启与中国的服务贸易协议，而且北京方面始终存在军事行动的威胁。</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Jan 2024 06:20:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwans-new-president-faces-tough-time-with-china-pressure-no-parliament-2024-01-14/</guid></item><item><title>朝鲜发射导弹，紧张局势升级，部长将访问俄罗斯</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/north-korea-fires-missile-south-korea-says-2024-01-14/</link><description>韩国表示，朝鲜周日在其东海岸发射了一枚明显的中程导弹，平壤最近发射了洲际弹道导弹及其第一颗军事间谍卫星，紧张局势加剧。</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Jan 2024 06:06:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/north-korea-fires-missile-south-korea-says-2024-01-14/</guid></item><item><title>中方反对日方向台湾当选总统贺电</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-opposes-japans-congratulatory-message-taiwan-president-elect-2024-01-14/</link><description>中国驻日本大使馆周日表示，“坚决反对”日本外务大臣上川洋子祝贺台湾新当选总统赖清德的声明。</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Jan 2024 04:19:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-opposes-japans-congratulatory-message-taiwan-president-elect-2024-01-14/</guid></item><item><title>台湾新当选总统赖清德将面临中国的愤怒</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/taiwan-president-elect-lai-face-chinas-ire-after-victory-2024-01-13/</link><description>赖在竞选期间多次表示，他希望与中国保持现状，并提出与北京对话。但在北京看来，他是一个分裂主义者，是一个“彻头彻尾的麻烦制造者”。</description><pubDate>Sat, 13 Jan 2024 13:18:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/taiwan-president-elect-lai-face-chinas-ire-after-victory-2024-01-13/</guid></item><item><title>西藏不是焦点，镇压持续存在：流亡前领导人</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/tibetan-issues-not-focus-repression-persists-exiled-former-leader-2024-01-13/</link><description>西藏流亡政府前领导人周六表示，国际上对西藏困境的讨论越来越少，但镇压仍在继续，中国正在将其在其他地区的做法应用到其他地区。</description><pubDate>Sat, 13 Jan 2024 07:22:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/tibetan-issues-not-focus-repression-persists-exiled-former-leader-2024-01-13/</guid></item><item><title>布林肯与中国官员讨论人权、台海问题</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/blinken-raises-human-rights-issues-meeting-with-senior-chinese-official-2024-01-13/</link><description>美国国务院表示，美国国务卿安东尼·布林肯周五在华盛顿会见中国高级官员刘建超时表达了对中国人权问题的担忧，并补充说，他们还讨论了“维护台湾海峡的和平与稳定”。</description><pubDate>Sat, 13 Jan 2024 00:50:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/blinken-raises-human-rights-issues-meeting-with-senior-chinese-official-2024-01-13/</guid></item><item><title>台湾选民拒绝中国，执政党获得第三个总统任期</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/polls-open-taiwans-critical-elections-watched-closely-by-china-2024-01-13/</link><description>赖清德领导的政党主张台湾的独立身份，拒绝中国的领土主张，正在寻求第三次连任。北京将这次选举视为战争与和平之间的选择。</description><pubDate>Sat, 13 Jan 2024 00:06:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/polls-open-taiwans-critical-elections-watched-closely-by-china-2024-01-13/</guid></item><item><title>中国敦促加强房地产业融资协调</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-urges-better-financing-coordination-housing-sector-2024-01-12/</link><description>在政策制定者努力重振低迷的房地产市场之际，中国住房和城乡建设部和金融监管机构要求地方政府更好地与金融机构协调，为房地产项目提供融资支持。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jan 2024 12:40:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-urges-better-financing-coordination-housing-sector-2024-01-12/</guid></item><item><title>中国2023年银行贷款创历史新高，但经济仍举步维艰</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-2023-bank-lending-record-high-economy-still-struggling-2024-01-12/</link><description>12 月份中国新增银行贷款增幅低于预期，但由于央行保持宽松政策以支持意外不稳定的经济复苏，2023 年贷款创下新纪录。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jan 2024 11:26:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-2023-bank-lending-record-high-economy-still-struggling-2024-01-12/</guid></item><item><title>在与中国的月球竞赛中，美国的挫折考验私营企业的作用</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/science/moon-race-with-china-us-setbacks-test-role-private-firms-2024-01-12/</link><description>本周美国在与中国的登月竞赛中遭遇的两次挫折说明了美国宇航局计划押注于严重依赖私营公司的新战略的风险。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jan 2024 11:08:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/science/moon-race-with-china-us-setbacks-test-role-private-firms-2024-01-12/</guid></item></channel></rss>